<p> Dream analysts believe that dreams reveal our inner thoughts, hopes and=
 fears. </p><br>
<p> The meaning of dreams has begun to develop into a somewhat consistent p=
attern, so that there are even dream dictionaries available which offer com=
mon interpretations of specific themes, such as flying or eating. </p><br>
<p> There are literally thousands of things people dream about with interpr=
etations that can be hard to understand. That=E2=80=99s why it can make sen=
se to talk to a trained dream interpretation Expert on JustAnswer.com </p><=
