<p></p><h2>How to find out what your dreams are telling you</h2><br>
<p>Dream analysis answers at JustAnswer.com include things like: </p><br>
<ul>
<li> What a grandparent symbolizes in a dream in a hospital </li>
<li> What it means if you dream of your childhood bedroom or something simi=
lar </li>
<li> Why people dream about former partners </li>
<li> How dreaming of a deceased family member can represent returned feelin=
gs from your past, or of generational trauma that is affecting you </li>
<li> What different animals represent in dreams </li>
<li> How dreams can help you heal from emotionally painful events </li>
</ul>
<p> Of course because the meaning of dreams can be unpleasant, you may not =
always get an answer from an Expert that you wanted to hear. But many thera=
pists believe that even unhappy dreams can give you a better understanding =
of your thoughts and feelings, even if you=E2=80=99ve buried them. </p><br>
<p> If you=E2=80=99d like to get a dream interpretation from an Expert, it =
will be helpful to write down the details of the dream, even details that y=
ou think might not mean anything. Trained dream analysts often recognize sm=
all details that help define an interpretation of a theme that has several =
different meanings. </p><br>
